short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Add YouTube videos to your Videocoleco collection

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Add YouTube videos to your Videocoleco collection with categories. 

The Videocoleco Extension allows users to easily add YouTube videos to their Videocoleco collection. By adding a convenient "Add To VCO" button to YouTube video thumbnails and video pages, users can quickly and seamlessly include their favorite videos in their Videocoleco collection directly from YouTube.

Videocoleco: One-Click YouTube Video Collector

Add your favorite YouTube videos to your personal Videocoleco library with a single click. Our extension adds an 'Add To VCO' button to YouTube pages, allowing you to effortlessly curate your video collection while you browse. Simplify your YouTube journey and never lose track of videos you love.
